VERSION 1
WHEN FILE_NAME_IS AndroidManifest.xml
WHEN CURRENT_FILE_MATCHES /android:usesCleartextTraffic\s*=\s*"(true|TRUE)"/i
OBSERVE PROJECT_HAS_GLOB **/network_security_config*.xml AS network_security_configs
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Cleartext traffic is enabled in the manifest and should be reviewed together with any network security configuration files.
TRACE Mobile RDL pilot checked the manifest hit and also looked for project-level network security configuration artifacts.
